{
  "id": "adv_card_kor_06_02",
  "title": "fran 2話 眠らせておく方がもったいない",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "嘘、嘘でしょ……！？\nバッグがない！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No way‚ you’re kidding‚ right…?\nMy bag is gone!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 4.9999996821
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "本当ですか！？　……って、あれ……\n俺の財布もなくなってる！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really!? …W-wait…\nMy wallet’s gone too!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.5666663487,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.933333079
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "きっとさっきの二人組よ！　やられた……！\nまだ近くにいるはず。追いかけるわよ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It must’ve been that pair from earlier! We’ve been had…！\nThey should still be close by. Let’s chase after them!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.9666664123,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.0666664123
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……見失った……\nああもう、久しぶりの海外だから油断したわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh… We lost them…\nUgh‚ I let my guard down because it’s been a while since I’ve been abroad…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.933333079,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんといると、遭難するわ\nスリに遭うわ……ろくなことがないですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whenever I’m with {user}-san… I get stranded‚\nrobbed… nothing good ever happens……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.6333321888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.6333340961
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "申し訳ないです、確かに俺の油断もありました……\nええと、とにかく落ち着いて、一度ホテルに……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sorry‚ I definitely let my guard down too…\nUm‚ anyway‚ let’s calm down and head back to the hotel…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.0999988555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "その前に警察ですね。被害届を出さないと\n対処の仕方は知ってますから、大丈夫ですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Before that‚ we need to go to the police and file a report.\nI know how to do that‚ so it’s no problem.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.5333319346,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.5666671752
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（franさん、海外に慣れてるだけあって）\n（落ち着いてるなぁ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Fran-san is so calm… Maybe because she is）\n（used to being abroad. ）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "ただ問題は、もしバッグが戻ってこなかった時\n滞在費もなしに、どうやって過ごすかですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The problem is‚ if my bag doesn’t come back‚\nhow are we going to get by without any money…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.1333352407,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.6666694641
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさんとkanaさんにお金を借りるのは\nどうですか？　日本に戻れば返せますし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How about borrowing money from miho-san and kana-san?\nWe can pay them back when we return to Japan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.9333342235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.2666689555
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "それ、本気で言ってます？\nあいつらに借りを作るなんて、ぜっっったいに嫌です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you serious?\nI would never‚ ever borrow money from them!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.767848216,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.5333356221
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "こんな状況でも、頼りたくないんですね\nでも、それならどうすれば……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even in this situation‚ you don’t want to rely on them.\nBut then what should we do…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.2000003815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.7000007628
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "仕方ない。後でこっちにいる知り合いに連絡します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It can’t be helped. I’ll contact an acquaintance here later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.7000007628,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.7333340961
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "誰か知り合いがいるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you know someone here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.7333340961,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "モデル時代からの知り合いがいるんです。こんな状況\n伝えにくいですけど、背に腹は代えられませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know someone from my modeling days. It’s hard\nto tell her about this situation‚ but I have no choice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.7666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.0500007628
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.0500007628
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "『もしもし？　久しぶり、カミーユ。元気だった？\nいきなりごめんね。実は――』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "‘Hello? It’s been a while‚ Camille. How have you been?\nSorry for calling out of the blue‚ actually…’",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.5333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.6333361306
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "『――という訳で、散々な目に遭ってるの\nそれでなんだけど……え？　うん、うん……』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "‘…So as I was saying‚ things are a complete mess.\nAnyway… Huh? Yeah‚ yeah…’",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.1666690826,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "『ありがとう。ちょっと確認してみるわね』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "‘Thanks. I’ll check it out.’",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.2000027972,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4299.996821500003,
          "startTime": 131.4999996187
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "なんとおっしゃっているんですか？\nフランス語はさっぱりで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What did she say?\nI don’t understand French at all…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.5666589101,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "「会うついでに、モデルの仕事をしないか」\nって誘われました。ギャラも出るみたいなんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Would you like to do some modeling work when you come see me?”\nShe asked. It seems like I’d get paid too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.4666589101,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "え、モデルの仕事？　どういうことですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait‚ modeling work? What do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.3666592914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.4999926248
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "ちょうどこれから、知人が主催する\nファッションショーが開かれるらしいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Apparently‚ there’s a fashion show\nthat my acquaintance is hosting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.8333255768,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 151.4666592914
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "でも、急な体調不良の欠員が出たらしくて\n「かわりに出てもらえるならぜひ」ですって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But someone suddenly got sick and can't make it‚\nso she said \"Please come to cover if you’re okay\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.9666589101,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_02-kor016.m4a",
      "text": "交渉してみたんですけど、私達の事情を考慮して\n報酬はその場で支払ってくれることになりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I negotiated‚ and considering our situation‚\nshe agreed to pay me on the spot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.5999912262,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 165.8666582742
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
